subject: use std::string wrapper for raw string
commitMessage:
use std::string wrapper for raw string

This patch fixes below error when we upgraded boost version to the
latest.

matched types 'const std::geometric_distribution<_IntType>' and 'const
char [10]'

Change-Id: Ib69347789e659ce3edaecf97c611ff97648e7bb0
Signed-off-by: Chanho Park <chanho61.park@samsung.com>

subject: Specialize stream output for shared_ptr<void> (fixed)
commitMessage:
Specialize stream output for shared_ptr<void> (fixed)

This patch was picked up from openSUSE's libzypp git[1]. This patch can
resolve below error when we upgrade the boost library to the latest
version.

note:   mismatched types 'const
std::piecewise_linear_distribution<_RealType>' and 'void*'
return str << (void*)obj.get();

[1]: https://github.com/openSUSE/libzypp.git

Change-Id: I333dee0c91065e0b69170713f65ed60eac04aa88
Signed-off-by: Chanho Park <chanho61.park@samsung.com>
